 _load="1"/> <div class="tip tip_4 aimg_tip" id="aimg_7600209_menu" style="display: none; position: absolute;"><div class="tip_c xs0"></div><div class="tip_horn"></div></div></ignore_js_op></span><br/><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff"><br/></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff">【ggokkio咕咕店】好看又超级美味的韩国小店，番茄辣意面味道好棒，咖喱饭沙拉也都很可口。炸鸡肉质鲜嫩，香脆可口，香辣炸鸡和三口辣面辣的后劲超足，饮料很小清新啊</span><br/><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff"><br/></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff">人均:50元</span><br/><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff"><br/></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff">地址：天鹅湖万达金街三楼</span><br/><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff"><br/><ignore_js_op><img width="605" title="2.jpg" class="zoom" id="aimg_7600210" alt="2.jpg" src="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/141041tlpzcfsps0p7essr.jpg" lazyloaded="true" aid="7600210" zoomfile="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/141041tlpzcfsps0p7essr.jpg" file="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/141041tlpzcfsps0p7essr.jpg" inpost="1" _load="1"/> <div class="tip tip_4 aimg_tip" id="aimg_7600210_menu" style="display: none; position: absolute;"><div class="tip_c xs0"></div><div class="tip_horn"></div></div></ignore_js_op><br/><br/></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff">【咖啡陪你】咖啡陪你(Caffebene很有feel的一家店~这家店原是韩国的，随着韩剧的风靡在中国开了不少分店。甜点简餐咖啡都有，华夫饼是别人推荐的，味道好好，草莓，蓝莓的都有。酱都次要的，主要是华夫饼好吃。推荐双重绿茶，香蕉华夫饼</span><br/><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff"><br/></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff">人均:40元</span><br/><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff"><br/></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff">地址:三孝口新华书店一楼</span><br/><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff"><br/><ignore_js_op><img width="434" title="3.jpg" class="zoom" id="aimg_7600211" alt="3.jpg" src="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/141042med2fi898dk9kzzm.jpg" lazyloaded="true" aid="7600211" zoomfile="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/141042med2fi898dk9kzzm.jpg" file="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/141042med2fi898dk9kzzm.jpg" inpost="1" _load="1"/> <div class="tip tip_4 aimg_tip" id="aimg_7600211_menu" style="display: none; position: absolute;"><div class="tip_c xs0"></div><div class="tip_horn"></div></div></ignore_js_op><br/><br/></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff">【韩国宇正年糕料理】虽刚开不久，人气火爆的很！饭点去吃都要排会队！多数都是女孩子！估摸着因为老板是个帅气的欧巴！主打年糕：奶酪年糕，芝士年糕，海鲜年糕，部队年糕等等！味道不错，吃货们反馈都很好</span><br/><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff"><br/></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff">人均:40元左右</span><br/><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff"><br/></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff">地址:天鹅湖万达室外步行街三楼</span><br/><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff"><br/><ignore_js_op><img width="431" title="4.jpg" class="zoom" id="aimg_7600212" alt="4.jpg" src="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/141042v9qfrtob85hqo20v.jpg" lazyloaded="true" aid="7600212" zoomfile="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/141042v9qfrtob85hqo20v.jpg" file="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/141042v9qfrtob85hqo20v.jpg" inpost="1" _load="1"/> <div class="tip tip_4 aimg_tip" id="aimg_7600212_menu" style="display: none; position: absolute;"><div class="tip_c xs0"></div><div class="tip_horn"></div></div></ignore_js_op><br/><br/></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff">【老爹米肠馆】有韩国欧巴的正宗韩国餐馆！在这里吃饭很有感觉的，米肠火锅味道超赞，汤是炖的，味道很纯很浓郁。推荐炒米肠、米肠火锅、泡菜饼、章鱼面、烤五花肉</span><br/><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff"><br/></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff">人均:45元</span><br/><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff"><br/></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑font-size:12pxcolor:#0000ff">地址:瑶海区物流大道与五里山路交口</span><br/><span style="font-family:微软雅黑fon