08080">1.把除黄油外的所有材料揉成面团，再加入黄油揉至出手套膜。</span></strong></div><span style="font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312font-size:24px"><strong><ignore_js_op><img width="529" title="1 (2).jpg" class="zoom" id="aimg_7600872" alt="1 (2).jpg" src="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160604dsgbg3kka1kxdiax.jpg" lazyloaded="true" aid="7600872" zoomfile="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160604dsgbg3kka1kxdiax.jpg" file="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160604dsgbg3kka1kxdiax.jpg" inpost="1" _load="1"/> <div class="tip tip_4 aimg_tip" id="aimg_7600872_menu" style="display: none; position: absolute;"><div class="tip_c xs0"></div><div class="tip_horn"></div></div></ignore_js_op><br/><br/></strong></span><div align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312font-size:24pxcolor:#008080">2.面团发酵到原来的2.5倍大，均分成小面团，盖上保鲜膜松驰15分钟。</span></strong></div><span style="font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312font-size:24px"><strong><ignore_js_op><img width="529" title="1 (4).jpg" class="zoom" id="aimg_7600874" alt="1 (4).jpg" src="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160605yupnhwy8aayszsg7.jpg" lazyloaded="true" aid="7600874" zoomfile="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160605yupnhwy8aayszsg7.jpg" file="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160605yupnhwy8aayszsg7.jpg" inpost="1" _load="1"/> <div class="tip tip_4 aimg_tip" id="aimg_7600874_menu" style="display: none; position: absolute;"><div class="tip_c xs0"></div><div class="tip_horn"></div></div></ignore_js_op><br/><br/></strong></span><div align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312font-size:24pxcolor:#008080">3.将小面团进行排气、收圆、整形，放入烤盘中。</span></strong></div><span style="font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312font-size:24px"><strong><ignore_js_op><img width="529" title="1 (5).jpg" class="zoom" id="aimg_7600875" alt="1 (5).jpg" src="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160605yymmtjt1r9dyqj1m.jpg" lazyloaded="true" aid="7600875" zoomfile="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160605yymmtjt1r9dyqj1m.jpg" file="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160605yymmtjt1r9dyqj1m.jpg" inpost="1" _load="1"/> <div class="tip tip_4 aimg_tip" id="aimg_7600875_menu" style="display: none; position: absolute;"><div class="tip_c xs0"></div><div class="tip_horn"></div></div></ignore_js_op><br/><br/></strong></span><div align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312font-size:24pxcolor:#008080">4.进行第二次发酵。</span></strong></div><span style="font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312font-size:24px"><strong><ignore_js_op><img width="529" title="1 (6).jpg" class="zoom" id="aimg_7600876" alt="1 (6).jpg" src="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/1606056i7x157ibf87v2n8.jpg" lazyloaded="true" aid="7600876" zoomfile="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/1606056i7x157ibf87v2n8.jpg" file="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/1606056i7x157ibf87v2n8.jpg" inpost="1" _load="1"/> <div class="tip tip_4 aimg_tip" id="aimg_7600876_menu" style="display: none; position: absolute;"><div class="tip_c xs0"></div><div class="tip_horn"></div></div></ignore_js_op><br/><br/></strong></span><div align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312font-size:24pxcolor:#008080">5.发酵好的面团表面刷上全蛋液。</span></strong></div><span style="font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312font-size:24px"><strong><ignore_js_op><img width="529" title="1 (7).jpg" class="zoom" id="aimg_7600877" alt="1 (7).jpg" src="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160605mnnahpdpddd34wfn.jpg" lazyloaded="true" aid="7600877" zoomfile="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160605mnnahpdpddd34wfn.jpg" file="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160605mnnahpdpddd34wfn.jpg" inpost="1" _load="1"/> <div class="tip tip_4 aimg_tip" id="aimg_7600877_menu" style="display: none; position: absolute;"><div class="tip_c xs0"></div><div class="tip_horn"></div></div></ignore_js_op><br/><br/></strong></span><div align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312font-size:24pxcolor:#008080">6.挤上装饰糊，装饰糊的做法：将装饰材料中的黄油和糖打至蓬松，分两次加入全蛋液，最后筛入面粉混和均匀，装入裱花袋即可。</span></strong></div><span style="font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312font-size:24px"><strong><ignore_js_op><img width="529" title="1 (8).jpg" class="zoom" id="aimg_7600878" alt="1 (8).jpg" src="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/1606062cz3ymt4haxizaj3.jpg" lazyloaded="true" aid="7600878" zoomfile="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/1606062cz3ymt4haxizaj3.jpg" file="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/1606062cz3ymt4haxizaj3.jpg" inpost="1" _load="1"/> <div class="tip tip_4 aimg_tip" id="aimg_7600878_menu" style="display: none; position: absolute;"><div class="tip_c xs0"></div><div class="tip_horn"></div></div></ignore_js_op><br/><br/></strong></span><div align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312font-size:24pxcolor:#008080">7.撒上白芝麻。</span></strong></div><span style="font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312font-size:24px"><strong><ignore_js_op><img width="529" title="1 (9).jpg" class="zoom" id="aimg_7600879" alt="1 (9).jpg" src="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160606zo1f0ok5d5o4veof.jpg" lazyloaded="true" aid="7600879" zoomfile="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160606zo1f0ok5d5o4veof.jpg" file="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/160606zo1f0ok5d5o4veof.jpg" inpost="1" _load="1"/> <div class="tip tip_4 aimg_tip" id="aimg_7600879_menu" style="display: none; position: absolute;"><div class="tip_c xs0"></div><div class="tip_horn"></div></div></ignore_js_op><br/><br/></strong></span><div align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:楷体, 楷体_GB2312font-size:24pxcolor:#008080">8.烤箱180度预热，中层18分钟。</span></strong></div><div align="left"><strong><ignore_js_op><img width="529" title="1 (11).jpg" class="zoom" id="aimg_7600881" alt="1 (11).jpg" src="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/16060600ti9vt7rissl1wb.jpg" lazyloaded="true" aid="7600881" zoomfile="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/16060600ti9vt7rissl1wb.jpg" file="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201410/13/16060600ti9vt7rissl1wb.jpg" inpost="1" _load="1"/> <div class="tip tip_4 aimg_tip" id="aimg_7600881_menu" style="display: none; position: absolute;"><div class="tip_c xs0"></div><div class="tip_horn"></div><