(9, '“邂逅合肥最美教师”活动拉开帷幕啦', 1, 2, '<p><em>本帖最后由 灰太狼蝈蝈 于 2014-9-10 09:50 编辑 <br/><br/></em></p><div align="center"><ignore_js_op><em><img width="700" title="教师节大图.jpg" class="zoom" id="aimg_7498666" alt="教师节大图.jpg" src="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201409/10/09474925fvffti1l1zkblh.jpg" lazyloaded="true" aid="7498666" zoomfile="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201409/10/09474925fvffti1l1zkblh.jpg" file="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201409/10/09474925fvffti1l1zkblh.jpg" inpost="1"/></em> <div class="tip tip_4 aimg_tip" id="aimg_7498666_menu" style="display: none; position: absolute;"><div class="tip_c xs0"></div><div class="tip_horn"></div></div></ignore_js_op></div><p><span style="font-size:18pxcolor:#800080"><strong>教师是火种，点燃了学生的心灵之火；教师是石级，承受着学生一步步踏实地向上攀登。美好的未来都离不开老师的教诲。9月10日，在第30个教师节来临之际，<a href="http://bbs.hefei.cc/" target="_blank"><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="color:#0066cc">合肥</span></span></a>论坛教育频道携手古井原浆和拜尔口腔联合开展的“邂逅合肥最美教师”活动拉开帷幕。活动中，网友代表将一份份薄礼陆续送入到老师的手中，感谢最亲爱的老师对我们孜孜不倦的教诲。</strong></span><br/><ignore_js_op><img width="83" title="动图美瓶.jpg" class="zoom" id="aimg_7498657" alt="动图美瓶.jpg" src="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201409/10/094315v8nfiikqn5twokc5.jpg" lazyloaded="true" aid="7498657" zoomfile="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201409/10/094315v8nfiikqn5twokc5.jpg" file="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201409/10/094315v8nfiikqn5twokc5.jpg" inpost="1" _load="1"/> <div class="tip tip_4 aimg_tip" id="aimg_7498657_menu" style="display: none; position: absolute;"><div class="tip_c xs0"></div><div class="tip_horn"></div></div></ignore_js_op><span style="font-size:18pxcolor:#800080"><strong><br/><div align="center"><strong>我们来到了合肥市阳光小学，“邂逅合肥最美教师”——陈万霞</strong></div></strong></span></p><div align="center"><ignore_js_op><img width="150" title="气球动图.gif" class="zoom" id="aimg_7498659" alt="气球动图.gif" src="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201409/10/094432cz5nsngwazj49nsq.gif" lazyloaded="true" aid="7498659" zoomfile="http://img3.hefei.cc/forum/201409/10/094432cz5nsngwazj49nsq.gif