k.htm?lemmaId=122431" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); text-decoration: none;">厨房</a>环境的改善，皮阿诺携手影帝<a class="ed_inner_link" target="_blank" href="http://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=257194&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); text-decoration: none;">陈宝国</a>先生为<a class="ed_inner_link" href="http://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=122771" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); text-decoration: none;">品牌</a>代言；并发起8月8日中国“<a class="ed_inner_link" target="_blank" href="http://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=8979928&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); text-decoration: none;">丈夫节</a>”倡议，为加强沟通消除家庭矛盾，共建和谐<a class="ed_inner_link" target="_blank" href="http://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=76066884&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); text-decoration: none;">幸福家</a>，提供了全新的思路和借鉴。</p><p style="text-align: left; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">多年来，皮阿诺始终关注<a class="ed_inner_link" href="http://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=6348052" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); text-decoration: none;">中国家庭</a>的<a class="ed_inner_link" href="http://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=122431" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); text-decoration: none;">厨房</a>需求，依托自主研发、坚持原创设计，每年都为终端奉献数套<a class="ed_inner_link" href="http://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=75854423" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); text-decoration: none;">经典设计</a>，“<a class="ed_inner_link" href="http://baike.sogou.com/lemma/Sho