(6, 1, 8, '开学季：香甜滋味椰浆芒果饭', '2014/10/15/thumb_543e20b4b19f7.jpg', '<h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;color:#000000;font-family:微软雅黑"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=74cf69a20102v3xu&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0028CUvMgy6MMTa1xyd85" target="_blank"><img title="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" alt="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" src="http://s6.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMTa1xyd85&690" action-type="show-slide" action-data="http%3A%2F%2Fs6.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F0028CUvMgy6MMTa1xyd85%26690" real_src="http://s6.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMTa1xyd85&amp;690"/></a><br/><br/></span><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=74cf69a20102v3xu&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0028CUvMgy6MMT06Ba8f8" target="_blank"><img name="image_operate_53911413207104933" width="550" height="830" title="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" alt="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" src="http://s9.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMT06Ba8f8&690" real_src="http://s9.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMT06Ba8f8&amp;690"/></a><br/><br/><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=74cf69a20102v3xu&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0028CUvMgy6MMT0aheEa0" target="_blank"><img name="image_operate_16911413207121485" width="550" height="830" title="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" alt="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" src="http://s1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMT0aheEa0&690" real_src="http://s1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMT0aheEa0&amp;690"/></a><br/><br/><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=74cf69a20102v3xu&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0028CUvMgy6MMT0gGGG9e" target="_blank"><img name="image_operate_62361413207198627" width="550" height="830" title="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" alt="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" src="http://s15.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMT0gGGG9e&690" real_src="http://s15.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMT0gGGG9e&amp;690"/></a></span></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;<wbr/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">椰浆的芳香，芒果的香甜</span></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">二种热带水果独有的香味交融</span></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">让这道椰浆芒果饭，香甜软糯中有着浓浓的热带风情</span></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">做为泰式美食的代表</span></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">这道椰浆芒果饭是去泰式餐厅必点的一道</span></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">也是我最爱的早餐之一</span></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">别看它是泰式餐厅的招牌，其实自已在家做也很容易</span></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">备齐了椰浆，芒果，再有<span>Lekue</span>料理盒帮忙</span></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">用微波炉加热，几分钟的时间，香甜美味的早餐就可以享用了</span></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;<wbr/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=74cf69a20102v3xu&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0028CUvMgy6MMT0jsyM64" target="_blank"><img name="image_operate_25621413207454383" width="550" height="830" title="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" alt="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" src="http://s5.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMT0jsyM64&690" real_src="http://s5.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMT0jsyM64&amp;690"/></a></span></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;<wbr/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=74cf69a20102v3xu&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0028CUvMgy6MMT0mL2Cce" target="_blank"><img name="image_operate_57611413207455210" width="550" height="830" title="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" alt="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" src="http://s15.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMT0mL2Cce&690" real_src="http://s15.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMT0mL2Cce&amp;690"/></a></span></span></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;<wbr/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=74cf69a20102v3xu&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0028CUvMgy6MMT0dwfbe5" target="_blank"><span style="font-family:宋体"><img name="image_operate_64221413207456130" width="550" height="830" title="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" alt="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" src="http://s6.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMT0dwfbe5&690" real_src="http://s6.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMT0dwfbe5&amp;690"/></span></a></span></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;<wbr/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=74cf69a20102v3xu&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0028CUvMgy6MMT0tu5E0e" target="_blank"><img name="image_operate_4591413207457019" width="550" height="830" title="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" alt="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" src="http://s15.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMT0tu5E0e&690" real_src="http://s15.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MMT0tu5E0e&amp;690"/></a></span></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;<wbr/></h2><h2 style="text-align: center; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;<wbr/><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">椰浆芒果饭（<span>3</span>人份）</span></h2><h2 style="text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">材料：糯米<span>200g</span>，椰浆<span>200+50g</span>，白砂糖<span>20g</span>，盐<span>3g</span>，芒果<span>1</span>个。</span></h2><h2 style="text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">做法：</span></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span><span style="font-family:宋体">1.</span><span new="" times="">&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/></span></span></span> &nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">糯米提前一晚浸泡，泡好后将泡米的水倒掉。</span></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span><span style="font-family:宋体">2.</span><span new="" times="">&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/></span></span></span> &nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">椰浆加糖和盐放小锅中热至融化。</span></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span><span style="font-family:宋体">3.</span><span new="" times="">&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/></span></span></span> &nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">用<span>200g</span>煮好的椰浆加入泡好的糯米中。</span></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span><span style="font-family:宋体">4.</span><span new="" times="">&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/></span></span></span> &nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">料理盒盖好，放进微波炉中。</span></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span><span style="font-family:宋体">5.</span><span new="" times="">&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/></span></span></span> &nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">高火加热<span>7</span>分钟，至糯米煮熟。</span></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span><span style="font-family:宋体">6.</span><span new="" times="">&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/></span></span></span> &nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">芒果去皮，一半用料理机打成浆，一半切片用模具切成心型。</span></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span><span style="font-family:宋体">7.</span><span new="" times="">&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/></span></span></span> &nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">煮好的糯米饭拌松后装入碗中，倒扣在盘子里。</span></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span><span style="font-family:宋体">8.</span><span new="" times="">&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/></span></span></span> &nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">摆上切好的心型芒果片，淋上余下的<span>50g</span>椰浆，再把打好的芒果浆点缀在糯米饭边上就可以了。</span></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;">&nbsp;<wbr/></h2><h2 style="text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">TIPS:</span></h2><h2 style="text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span><span style="font-family:宋体">1.</span><span new="" times="">&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/></span></span></span> &nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">椰浆在一些大型的超市有售，如果买不到也可以椰奶代替，只是香味会淡一些。</span></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span><span style="font-family:宋体">2.</span><span new="" times="">&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/></span></span></span> &nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">微波炉的功率不一样，加热的时间也会不同，请依实际情况调整加热时间。</span></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><span><span style="font-family:宋体">3.</span><span new="" times="">&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/>&nbsp;<wbr/></span></span></span> &nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;font-family:宋体">芒果打成浆我是为了更美观，切片，切块搭配一起吃是一样的。</span>&nbsp;<wbr/></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=74cf69a20102v3xu&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0028CUvMgy6MNwacHxv49" target="_blank"><img name="image_operate_19741413241310788" title="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" alt="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" src="http://s10.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MNwacHxv49&690" real_src="http://s10.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MNwacHxv49&amp;690"/></a></span></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=74cf69a20102v3xu&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0028CUvMgy6MNwaj5la7c" target="_blank"><img name="image_operate_56871413241317761" title="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" alt="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" src="http://s13.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MNwaj5la7c&690" real_src="http://s13.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MNwaj5la7c&amp;690"/></a></span></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=74cf69a20102v3xu&url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0028CUvMgy6MNwamSUtb5" target="_blank"><img name="image_operate_20831413241318806" title="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" alt="#新浪美食开学季#早餐的香甜滋味—椰浆芒果饭" src="http://s6.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MNwamSUtb5&690" real_src="http://s6.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0028CUvMgy6MNwamSUtb5&amp;690"/></a></span></h2><h2 style="margin: auto 0px auto 24px; text-align: justify; line-height: 20px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="color: r